<p><strong>Carinthia &amp; BKK Resort cards</strong> FREE for all guests, includes:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Free</strong> use of cable cars</li>
<li><strong>Free</strong> boat trip on Lake Millslätter and others</li>
